s and 71% of\nin-app communications between riders and driver-partners adopted the smart\nreplies to speedup the communication process.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 18 Jul 2019 17:19:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-19"}
