ally,\ninspired by Young tableaux, we introduce a technical tool which may be of\nindependent interest: it is a \"canonical\" way of writing any monomial in any\ngiven set of polynomials. Our methods are characteristic--free.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 18 Jul 2019 17:30:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 5 Aug 2019 21:27:42 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 2 Jun 2020 19:06:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-04"}
