nce with n < 2 for x = 0.20 and 0.30. These low-T\nNFL behaviors observed in the Cp and rho measurements are most evident near the\nquantum-critical concentration x ~ 0.3 at which a T = 0 composition-induced\ntransition from the AFM phase to the PM phase occurs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 18 Jul 2019 18:38:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-09"}
