tly translated 95% of the use case specification steps into formal\nconstraints required for test data generation; furthermore, it generated test\ncases that exercise not only all the test scenarios manually implemented by\nexperts, but also some critical scenarios not previously considered.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 19 Jul 2019 12:47:58 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 18 May 2020 17:25:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-19"}
