d furthermore accompanied by the\nproposal of an optional procedure to verify strong equilibrium of the axial\nforce along the beam element, which is usually not accomplished by DB beam\nelements. Given a fixed mesh discretisation the performance of the FSDB beam\nelement is compared with the DB approach to show the better accuracy of the\nproposed element.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 19 Jul 2019 13:37:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-04"}
